      <h1 style = "text-shadow:2px 2px 4px #ffffff; font-size: 30px;"><b>Frequently Asked Questions</b></h1> <br><br>

      <div class="faq">
        <b>How do I commission an artwork?</b><br><br>
        <i>Click on the "Guidelines" Tab and download the form at the bottom of the page.</i><br><br><br><br><br>

        <b>Can the artwork be personalised?</b><br><br>
        <i>Definitely! Everything can be fully personalized and customized according to individual specifications – body pose, attire, background etc. Additionally, if you wish, a brief caption or description can written on it.</i><br><br><br><br><br>
        
        <b>Are the artworks handmade?</b><br><br>
        <i>All artworks are 100% hand-drawn with love by me using a digital tablet or a traditional medium.</i><br><br><br><br><br>
        
        <b>Can I include a background?</b><br><br>
       <i>You can choose either a simple or detailed background. You can include a photo of the background in your email.<br>
        (*Please note that the complexity will affect the total price.)</i><br><br><br><br><br>
        <img src= "output-onlinegiftools (6).gif" style= "width:300px; height:300px; float: right;">
        <b>Can I combine individual photos?</b><br><br> 
        <i> Yes! You can send individual photos and I can draw them together for you.</i><br><br><br><br><br> 

        <b>How do you deliver physical artworks?</b><br><br>
        
       <i>♡ International shipping is available<br><br>
          ♡ Shipping price depends on the distance, speed and courier chosen. You will be consulted by the artist to discuss which courier suits best for you.<br><br>
          ♡ If anything comes up that will slow the progress of the initially estimated delivery time I will let you know ASAP<br><br>
          ♡ You will receive tracking updates on your package once it's shipped.<br><br></i> 
          <br><br><br>
        <b>How do you deliver digital artworks?</b><br><br>
        <i>♡ You will receive a downloadable JPEG file that can be used digitally or for a high-quality print.<br><br>
          ♡ If you have any special requirements for dimensions, please let me know.</b></i><br><br>
